<plot>Manor of Redemption is a run down, 18th Century restorative clinic where wealthy eccentrics are exorcised of the evil of creative expression. An innocent young artist joins the last few inmates (an egotistical dandy, a has-been actress and a schizophrenic widow), and against a background of peculiar therapies, they reveal scraps of their interwoven histories through a series of metaphorical monologues on identity, ego and self image, whilst events and revelations are observed and guided by a mysterious masked figure in the attic.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?356750</url></doc>
